
  Usage:

    make <target> [FLAG1=...] [FLAG2=...]

  Targets:

    doctor           Check your system for potential problems.
    help             Show this help
    print-variables  Print all declared variables
    self-add         url=<url> [name=<string>] Add a makefile module (as git submodule)
    self-install     Install makefile modules
    self-update      Update all makefile modules
    test-included    Test target included
    test-root        test=true Test included root

  Flags:

    LOG_LEVEL              Set the log level (debug/info/warn/error/fatal default:info)
    MAKEFILE_EXCLUDE       Makefiles to be excluded (default "$(MAKEFILE_CORE)")
    MAKEFILE_INCLUDE       Makefiles to be included (default ".modules/*/Makefile", ".modules/*/*.{mk,make}")
    MAKEFILE_LOCAL         Optional Makefile loaded to override locally any value (default "Makefile.local")
    MAKEFILE_PATH          Main Makefile path
    MAKEFILE_UPDATER_URL   Upstream for core.mk used by make self-update
    TEST_FLAG_INCLUDED     Test flag included
    TEST_FLAG_ROOT         test=true Test Flag Root
    VERBOSE                Set the make output as verbose

